---
/**
 * rest-api/0007 · Figure 3 — the conditional GET: client echoes its stored ETag
 * in If-None-Match; a match returns 304 (no body), a change returns 200 with the
 * full body and a new ETag.
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from the source HTML (figure + svg + figcaption). Lives as an
 * .astro component for the kebab-case-SVG reason. The markers it references
 * (#arw, #arwG) come from the source's global hidden <svg>, which does not
 * travel with the figure, so they're inlined here in a local <defs>, fills/ids
 * verbatim.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 640 200"
        role="img"
        aria-label="Conditional GET: client sends If-None-Match with the stored ETag; if unchanged the server returns 304 with no body and the cache serves the stored copy; if changed it returns 200 with the new body and a new ETag"
    >
        <defs>
            <marker
                id="arw"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#6b675f"></path></marker
            >
            <marker
                id="arwG"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#2f5d3a"></path></marker
            >
        </defs>
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text
                x="320"
                y="18"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">THE CONDITIONAL GET — REVALIDATE WITHOUT RE-DOWNLOADING</text
            >
            <rect
                x="14"
                y="86"
                width="150"
                height="58"
                rx="9"
                fill="#f1eee2"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="89"
                y="110"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="12"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">Cache / client</text
            >
            <text x="89" y="127" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >holds ETag "v7"</text
            >
            <line x1="164" y1="106" x2="232" y2="106" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"
            ></line>
            <text x="198" y="98" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >If-None-Match: "v7"</text
            >
            <rect x="234" y="86" width="130" height="58" rx="9" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"></rect>
            <text x="299" y="111" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" font-weight="700">Origin</text
            >
            <text x="299" y="128" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >compares ETags</text
            >
            <rect
                x="430"
                y="22"
                width="200"
                height="58"
                rx="9"
                fill="#eef5ee"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="530"
                y="44"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#2f5d3a">MATCH → 304</text
            >
            <text x="530" y="60" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#244a2e"
                >Not Modified · NO body</text
            >
            <text x="530" y="73" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#244a2e"
                >serve stored copy → save bandwidth</text
            >
            <rect x="430" y="150" width="200" height="58" rx="9" fill="#eef2f5" stroke="#1f3a5a"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="530"
                y="172"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#1f3a5a">CHANGED → 200</text
            >
            <text x="530" y="188" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#1f3a5a"
                >full body + new ETag</text
            >
            <text x="530" y="201" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#1f3a5a"
                >cache refreshes its copy</text
            >
            <path
                d="M 364 96 C 390 70, 405 58, 430 52"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                marker-end="url(#arwG)"></path>
            <path
                d="M 364 130 C 390 158, 405 170, 430 178"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#1f3a5a"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></path>
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        A <code>304</code> revalidates freshness for the price of headers — no entity body crosses the
        wire. That's the bandwidth saver behind every well-tuned cache.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
